.DS_Store

# Capacitor
# - `native/` is regenerated by `npm run build:native` on every build.
#   Codemagic re-runs it, so keeping it in git is just noise.
# - `ios/` is regenerated by `npx cap add ios` on every fresh build
#   (Codemagic's mac_mini_m2 instance is stateless). Codemagic runs
#   scripts/prepare-ios.sh which recreates it. Do not commit it.
native/
ios/
android/
# but keep our scripts + config
!capacitor.config.ts
!codemagic.yaml
!scripts/
